{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"Docs","description":"Everything you need to know about working with the Ghost professional publishing platform."}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Tools","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":null,"meta_description":null,"image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":null,"toc":null,"keywords":["Tools"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"chrome-extension\"><a href=\"#chrome-extension\" aria-label=\"chrome extension permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Chrome Extension</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/OctoLinker/OctoLinker\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">OctoLinker</a> — Links together, what belongs together</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/hide-files-on-github\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hide Files on GitHub</a> - Hide nonessential files from the GitHub file browser </li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/file-icon-for-github-gitl/ficfmibkjjnpogdcfhfokmihanoldbfe/related\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">File Icon for GitHub, GitLab and Bitbucket</a>，更好看的文件 icon</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/git-history-browser-exten/laghnmifffncfonaoffcndocllegejnf/related\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Git History Browser Extension</a>，可视化的方式显示文件修改历史</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"vs-code-plugin\"><a href=\"#vs-code-plugin\" aria-label=\"vs code plugin permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>VS Code Plugin</h2>\n<h3 id=\"html\"><a href=\"#html\" aria-label=\"html permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>HTML</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Auto Close Tag</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Auto Rename Tag</strong></li>\n<li><strong>htmltagwrap</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"css\"><a href=\"#css\" aria-label=\"css permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CSS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>CSS Modules</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Beautify</strong> - Beautify javascript, JSON, CSS, Sass, and HTML in Visual Studio Code.</li>\n<li><strong>Beautify css/sass/scss/less</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"js\"><a href=\"#js\" aria-label=\"js permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>JS</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Document This</strong></li>\n<li><strong>ESLint</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Prettier</strong> - Code formatter</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"editor\"><a href=\"#editor\" aria-label=\"editor permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Editor</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>GitLens</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Live Server</strong></li>\n<li><strong>npm-import-package-version</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Path Intellisense</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Markdown All in One</strong></li>\n<li><strong>REST Client</strong> - Send HTTP request and view the response in Visual Studio Code directly.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"theme\"><a href=\"#theme\" aria-label=\"theme permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3